odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 40 (YRG 40), Records of Yale clubs, societies, and organizations.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: The records in this collection are partially restricted. See Collection Contents for details.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Clubs, Societies, and Organizations at Yale Records (RU 56). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Yale University records are arranged and described at the accession level by the creating office. The University Archives creates collection level descriptive records, but typically does no further arrangement and description at the accession level.

originalsloc.head: Existence and Location of Originals
originalsloc.p: Records for several organizations have been removed from accession 19ND-A-377 and transferred to record units for their appropriate organization.
Records of the Thulia Boat Club, the Varuna Boat Club, the Glyuna Boat Club, and the Yale Navy, 1853-1896, are available on 1 microfilm reel, HM 161.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records consist of minutes of meetings, membership lists, correspondence, constitutions and bylaws, scrapbooks, library records, financial and business records, programs and invitations, certificates, articles and news clippings, reports, songbooks, notices, newsletters, and related materials documenting the organization, activities, and operations of various student, faculty, and staff organizations, and other Yale community groups.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The records are arranged by accession.

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition
acqinfo.p: Accession 2018-A-049 transferred from the Beinecke Rare Book and Manuscript Library, 2018.
